{"tid":2074204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"顏武周上咗維基百科首頁，大家有時間可以睇下","createTime":"2020-06-22T02:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T16:26:04.000Z","uid":71237,"like":98,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d76e2b8daf0f757a09e3eceb69501e1e9778491c","tid":2074204,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"有一班巴打一直喺維基百科默默努力，去記載反送中運動的人物和事件。<br />\n有巴打幫顏武周寫咗條目，大家想了解多啲佢嘅事蹟可以去睇下。<br />\n<a href=\"https://w.wiki/UpR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fw.wiki%2FUpR&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=5b8da3e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://w.wiki/UpR</a>"},{"pid":"6c73d0de62b59f9407f843f4efa23f32ac93f88c","tid":2074204,"uid":71237,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:38:17.000Z","msg":"如果你都想喺維基百科寫嘢，喺寫之前不妨睇下我們提供的新手教學。<br />\n因為維基百科的特徵就係任何人都可以修改，好多人擔心自己寫嘅嘢會俾五毛亂刪。<br />\n但其實只要你花半個鐘時間去了解咗基本規則，你就會知道點樣寫先唔會輕易被刪除。<br />\n（相反如果你唔了解基本規則，你寫嘅嘢太差勁，就算我係同路人都會想刪除你寫嘅嘢。）<br />\n<br />\n目前維基百科活躍寫反送中運動嘅香港人大概只有十幾個，人手真係嚴重不足。<br />\n我們需要更多新血加入，多你一個就真係好多。好多嘢你唔寫就真係永遠無人寫。<br />\n<br />\n如果你係新手，可以閱讀以下的新手教學：<br />\n維基百科戰線招募長期參與者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1</a><br />\n[教學] 如何成為維基百科撰寫師？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1595959/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你喺維基百科遇到問題，可以入telegram group搵其他資深維基人協助。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/J3cWeBaQbYp1etQ4MOBLFw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJ3cWeBaQbYp1etQ4MOBLFw&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=dc37c87d\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/J3cWeBaQbYp1etQ4MOBLFw</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你想幫手寫嘢/做資料搜集，可以入telegram channel，睇下有咩條目需要幫手。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=33423568\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAE8nDMP5qEHzdgBBQQ</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你用手機寫緊維基百科，覺得要引用資料好麻煩，可以用「維基百科引用助手 Bot」<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkwikiref_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkwikiref_bot&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=578963d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkwikiref_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n如果大家發現維基百科有嘢值得寫/有惡意破壞，可以用維基百科(Wikipedia)報料Bot向我地報告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wikiscout_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwikiscout_bot&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=f20776b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wikiscout_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你想了解關於維基百科戰線的最新消息，可以like我地的Facebook page。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%B6%AD%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A-103027814743750/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%2599%25BE%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%25B7%259A-103027814743750%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=e645988f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%B6%AD%E5%9F%BA%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A-103027814743750/</a><br />\n<br />\n維基百科戰線運作示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WY1G6ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWY1G6ad.jpg&h=93cc57c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28486e9e335ada5e51886962b803e7fba7869480","tid":2074204,"uid":71237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T02:38:32.000Z","msg":"同埋維基百科戰線都需要宣傳師。<br />\n各位可唔可以幫手去唔同的渠道分享依個post，希望可以吸引到更多唔同background嘅人留意到維基百科戰線。<br />\n<br />\n因為我喺連登推post都已經推咗半年有多，但係都幾乎無人加入，我覺得喺連登宣傳已經去到盡頭。<br />\n我希望有宣傳師可以協助，呼籲更多人加入維基百科戰線。<br />\n（唔需要文筆叻，識得整合唔同新聞報導，用自己文字寫返出嚟就得。）"},{"pid":"0c843d6517cd4cf0f6c2a30690836246de408131","tid":2074204,"uid":10540,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"28486e9e335ada5e51886962b803e7fb